11
00:02:26.640 --> 00:02:28.640
我对世界从未放弃过希望
I have never given upon the world

12
00:02:28.710 --> 00:02:32.110
我相信上帝还未弃我而去
and I have faith that providence has not yet given up on me

13
00:02:33.150 --> 00:02:34.620
一艘船
A ship

14
00:02:38.760 --> 00:02:39.780
