那看起来很痛啊
That looks painful

61
00:10:45.180 --> 00:10:46.670
是啊
It is

62
00:10:47.010 --> 00:10:49.610
但不致命 我将它拔出来吧
But not mortal I will pull it through

63
00:10:51.820 --> 00:10:54.310
我招 什么都招
I'll talk I'll tell you everything

64
00:10:57.690 --> 00:11:01.320
这里这小岛上有探险家的黄金
There's There's a conquistador gold on the island

65
