我们中没有老大
We don't have a leader

68
00:11:08.970 --> 00:11:12.270
2死1伤
Two men dead one wounded

69
00:11:12.800 --> 00:11:15.100
他安全回到海滩上
and he's back safe on the beach

70
00:11:16.510 --> 00:11:18.670
依我看他就是老大
That sounds like a leader to me

71
