你的船在哪
Where's your ship

72
00:11:19.980 --> 00:11:22.340
没有大船只有我们来的那个单桅帆船
No ship just thesloop we came in

73
00:11:24.450 --> 00:11:25.780
谢谢你
Thank you

74
00:11:29.020 --> 00:11:30.420
不幸的是
Unfortunately

75
00:11:30.490 --> 00:11:32.820
星期五需要他的箭
Friday still needs his arrow

76
00:11:46.300 --> 00:11:48.240
星期五也可以穿外套
Friday could use a coat

77
00:11:49.540 --> 00:11:53.980
这位先生 很可惜不再需要外套了
This gentleman alas needs a coat no longer

78
00:11:55.650 --> 00:11:57.240
为什么他说话方式那么奇怪
Why doe she talk like that

79
00:11:57.310 --> 00:11:59.280
星期五需要这个星期五说过那个
"Friday needs this Friday says that"

80
00:11:59.350 --> 00:12:02.010
他在取笑我 他知道我不能叫出他的真名
He's making fun of me He knows I can't pronounce his real name

81
00:12:02.090 --> 00:12:04.180
- 你应该揍他  -是啊 我会试试的
- You should beat him  - Yeah I'll try that

82
00:12:04.250 --> 00:12:05.350
为什么叫星期五呢
But why Friday

83
00:12:05.420 --> 00:12:06.820
我在星期五找到他的
The day of the week I found him

84
00:12:06.890 --> 00:12:08.820
于是想把他训练成仆人
I had this idea I was going to train him as a servant

85
00:12:08.890 --> 00:12:10.550
至于他为什么一直跟着我我也不明白
Why he stuck with me I don't know

86
00:12:10.630 --> 00:12:12.360
你不能和野人做朋友
You can't make a friend of a savage

87
00:12:12.430 --> 00:12:16.530
那野人能懂12种不同语言
That savage can make himself understood in 12 different languages

88
