So he can't read for himself then eh

91
00:12:26.210 --> 00:12:27.270
不会
No

92
00:12:27.340 --> 00:12:29.470
是啊 野人
Yeah savages

93
00:12:31.150 --> 00:12:32.340
哇
Ow

94
00:12:36.350 --> 00:12:39.320
听着 2个人死了
Listen with two men dead

95
00:12:39.390 --> 00:12:41.120
现在船上有空余位置
you'll have space on the boat now

96
00:12:41.190 --> 00:12:42.890
你的脸皮真厚 一点不假
You've got a thick skin and no mistake

97
00:12:42.960 --> 00:12:44.660
我的子女有危险
My children are in danger

98
00:12:44.730 --> 00:12:46.130
我得回到英国去
and I need to get back to England

99
00:12:46.200 --> 00:12:48.320
别和这些船员走很郑重的建议哦
Well not with this crew and that's serious advice

100
00:12:48.400 --> 00:12:50.920
一旦找到黄金 人人安危难保
Soon as the gold's out the ground nobody's safe

101
00:12:51.000 --> 00:12:53.700
短兵相接 没有后路可退你和你的星期五
Daggers drawn and don't turn your back you and your man Friday

102
00:12:53.770 --> 00:12:55.070
我不想要你们的黄金
I don't want your gold

103
00:12:55.140 --> 00:12:57.570
你去跟那些西班牙渣子说好了
Explain that to the scum of the Spanish Main

104
00:12:57.640 --> 00:12:59.540
你会熬不过第一晚的
You'll not last the first night

105
00:13:02.550 --> 00:13:03.980
那么我会这么做
Then here's what I'll do

106
00:13:09.950 --> 00:13:12.110
没人会干扰你们的任务
No one will interfere with your mission

107
00:13:14.790 --> 00:13:16.690
你将看不到我们
You won't even see us

108
00:13:16.760 --> 00:13:18.890
但你得为我做件事
But do this one thing for me

109
00:13:19.530 --> 00:13:21.430
当你回到陆地上
When you return to the mainland

110
00:13:21.500 --> 00:13:24.190
告诉当权者这里有个岛
tell someone in authority that here is an island

111
00:13:24.270 --> 00:13:25.830
小岛上有个落难已久的男人
and on it is a man who's desperate

112
00:13:25.900 --> 00:13:28.030
迫切渴望回乡和心爱的人团聚
to get to his home and the ones he loves

113
00:13:29.210 --> 00:13:31.170
你会那么做吗
Will you dot hat for me

114
00:13:34.080 --> 00:13:36.340
这要求不算高吧
Surely that's not too much to ask

115
00:13:36.410 --> 00:13:39.180
20多年来没人尊重过我
No one's showed me respect in more than 20 years

116
00:13:40.820 --> 00:13:43.050
我 那个曾要开枪杀你的家伙
Me who tried to shoot you down

117
00:13:44.190 --> 00:13:45.660
嗯
Mmm

118
00:13:48.960 --> 00:13:51.220
我喜欢好故事
I love a good story

119
00:13:54.330 --> 00:13:58.060
