我们更喜欢"寻宝人"这个称呼
Ah we prefer"gentlemen of fortune"

130
00:14:31.220 --> 00:14:32.380
都没有一艘大船
With no ship

131
00:14:32.450 --> 00:14:35.180
命运使然 天有不测风云
Aye thanks to the small dip in our fortune

132
00:14:35.260 --> 00:14:37.950
大船在甘达海岸因事而破损
at the guns of the Guarda costa

133
