Show Mr Crusoe what'll happen if he doesn't help

145
00:15:57.040 --> 00:15:59.340
好吧 来吧
All right come on boy

146
00:15:59.470 --> 00:16:00.700
等一下
Hold

147
00:16:09.880 --> 00:16:11.650
太恐怖了
Strike me down

148
