我可不是这么想的
That was not really what I had in mind

151
00:16:59.970 --> 00:17:01.590
但我也跟你说清楚了吧
But is my point made

152
00:17:07.270 --> 00:17:09.570
我们看地图吧 好吧
Let's just look at the map all right

153
00:17:22.920 --> 00:17:26.480
看啊 这没有太多地标
See there's not many landmarks

154
00:17:26.560 --> 00:17:28.050
