in case we have to blast the treasure out of the ground

181
00:19:10.260 --> 00:19:11.320
看起来很重啊
Looks heavy

182
00:19:11.400 --> 00:19:12.730
是的
I suppose it is

183
00:19:12.800 --> 00:19:16.600
跟我讲讲 带你来这个岛的船呢
So tell me this ship that brought you to the island

184
00:19:16.670 --> 00:19:18.070
残骸在哪里
where's the wreck

185
00:19:18.140 --> 00:19:21.160
别提了 暴风雨摧毁了它  什么东西也没留下
Forget it Storms broke it up There's nothing left you can plunder

186
00:19:21.240 --> 00:19:22.870
真可怜
Ah pity

187
00:19:24.340 --> 00:19:26.110
在这之后会怎么对待我
So what happens to me after this

